                    </ol>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs">
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 border border-rose-200">Vekalet Borcu: 40.000 − 25.000 = 15.000 TL</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border border-emerald-200">Emanet Bakiye: −500 + 2.000 = 1.500 TL</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Senaryo 4 -->
                <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-custom mb-1">Senaryo 4: Ay Sonu Büro Giderleri</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 italic mb-3">Bu ay büro kirası 15.000 TL, asistan maaşı 12.000 TL ve kırtasiye 800 TL harcadın.</p>
