                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs">
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 border border-slate-200">Ücret Tahsilatı: 25.000 TL</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 border border-slate-200">Büro Gideri: 27.800 TL</span>
                        <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 border border-rose-200">Bu Ay Kâr: -2.800 TL (zarar)</span>
