                        <li>Tablodaki <strong>Vekalet Borcu</strong> ve <strong>Emanet Bakiye</strong> sütunlarına bak</li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                        <table class="w-full text-xs border border-slate-200 rounded-md">
                            <thead class="bg-slate-100"><tr><th class="px-2 py-1.5 text-left text-slate-500">Müvekkil</th><th class="px-2 py-1.5 text-left text-slate-500">Vekalet Borcu</th><th class="px-2 py-1.5 text-left text-slate-500">Emanet Bakiye</th></tr></thead>
                            <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
                                <tr><td class="px-2 py-1.5">Ahmet Yılmaz</td><td class="px-2 py-1.5 text-rose-600 font-medium">15.000 TL</td><td class="px-2 py-1.5 text-emerald-600 font-medium">1.500 TL</td></tr>
